I, cac van de trong convert:
1. to chuc bien de toi uu hoa code, khong bi lap lai trong qua trinh tao bonding
giai phap de xuat:
- su dung ky thuat loop chang han with_items, with_nested
- luu bien theo group neu su dung chung trong cac cum vi du CTL

2. thay doi ip cua remote host, lam cho inventory file thay doi.
giai phap de xuat:
- them vao local_action, add initial_ip voi ten CTL1 vao /etc/hosts.
- su dung ten CTL1 trong inventory thay vi ip cu the

3. reboot remote host
giai phap de xuat:
- su dung local_action, duoc huong dan o 2 link sau:
    + https://gist.github.com/infernix/a968f23c4f4e1d6723e4
    + http://www.linuxnix.com/ansible-reboot-server-in-play-book-and-wait-for-it-come-back/